Package: translateVTT
Title: Automatically translate VTT files
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: person("Vladimir", "Zhbanko", 
           email = "vladimir.zhbanko@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Package imports user files from a specified directory, extract text
    of closed captions, sends this text to Google Translate API retrieve back the
    translation and return original structure of the file. Then package will write
    vtt file back to the original directory.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.3)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    tibble,
    tidyverse,
    translateR (>= 1.0),
    utils
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
